Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,\N♪ Are the Crystal Gems
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,\N♪ We'll always save the day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.20,0:00:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,\NSteven: ♪ And if you think we can't
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,\N♪ We'll always find a way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,\N♪ That's why the people
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,\N♪ Of this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.21,0:00:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,\N♪ Believe in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,\N♪ Garnet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,\NAmethyst: ♪ Amethyst
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.55,0:00:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,\NPearl: ♪ And Pearl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,\NAnd Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 来了一个!石榴 许个愿吧!\NOoh -- there's one! Garnet, you gotta make a wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.66,0:00:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,闭上眼\NClose your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,全都闭上\NAll of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧好吧\NOkay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,现在许个愿望，别告诉我是什么\NNow make your wish, but don't tell me what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,石榴 你许了什么愿?\NGarnet, what did you wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我的愿望是\NI wished...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一颗流星 这样你就可以许愿了\Nfor another shooting star, so that you could make a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,哦我天\NOh, my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.31,0:00:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,石榴 愿望实现了!\NGarnet, it worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.12,0:00:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那个流星...是在尖叫吗\NIs that star... screaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:00:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那是啥?!\NWhat was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是脐脐!\NIt's Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是个红宝石\NThat's a ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得了吗?我给她们都起了名\NDon't you remember? I gave them all names.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这只叫脐脐，因为她宝石在肚脐上\NThis one's Navy, 'cause her gem is on her navel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我才明白过来\NOh. I finally get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 求求你\NOh, please, oh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,别把我送回母星!\NDon't make me go back to Homeworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.61,0:01:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和你们一起住在这里!\NOh, I just want to stay here with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这...还真出乎预料呢\NThis... is a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你想住在地球上?\NYou want to live on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊!其他红宝石都对我很坏\NYeah! All the other rubies are mean to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我就想找一个能做自己的地方\NI just want to be somewhere I can be myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们那么对你 你不生气吗?\NAnd you're not mad at us from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你是指什么?\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的 比如骗你去打棒球那次\NYou know, about tricking you into playing baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.10,0:01:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,棒球很好玩啊!\NThat was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还有那次紫晶扮成铁石英骗你们\NOr when Amethyst pretended to be Jasper.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我得承认 那个骗局挺机智的\NI gotta admit, that was pretty clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还有那次我把你们送进了太空\NOr when we blasted you all out into space and stole your ship
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,还偷了你们的太空船?\Nso you'd be stranded forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 我们当时在战斗嘛 可以理解\NWell, we were fighting, so it's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\NI don't know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是想用匕首戳你来着\NShe tried to stab you in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:01:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那是眼宝 不是脐脐\NThat was Eyeball, this is Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 她一直都是最可爱的那个\NShe always seemed really nice, actually!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢夸奖\NHey, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 从天上坠入人间的红宝石\NAnd, you know, a ruby falling from the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,发现新世界的美丽--\Ndiscovering this beautiful world --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这不就是你给我讲的故事吗\Nsounds a lot like a story you told me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 别说了\NOh, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!从这儿起就交给我吧!\NAh! Let me take it from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道有个地方绝对适合她!\NI know exactly where she'll fit in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 史蒂文宇宙 施展你的魔法吧\NAll right, Steven Universe, go work your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,总算有个可以许愿的星星了!\NFinally! There's a star to wish on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.51,0:02:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,橄榄石!青金石!\NPeridot, Lapis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-史蒂文!-史蒂文!\N-Steven! -Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,还有南瓜!我可没把你忘了!\NAnd Pumpkin! Can't forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你 又回来了\NWell, well, back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我们一起住在这儿就好了嘛\NYou should just move in with us at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,其实 可能不是我\NActually, maybe not me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知道有其他人想在这里住哦!\Nbut I know someone else who might be interested!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你好!我是脐脐，母星来的难民!\NHi! I'm Navy, a refugee from Homeworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你们一样!哈哈哈!\NJust like you guys! Ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这个...\NSo, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候来地球的?\NWhen did you show up on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就今天!\NToday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,新室友!\NNew barnie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啥?!不行 等等\NWhat?! No, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:02:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,至少先商量一下吧?\NCan we talk about this first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊!是是是 当然了!\NYeah! Yeah, yeah, yeah, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.21,0:03:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我最爱商量了!\N I love talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哈?\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂文 这根本说不通\NSteven, this makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她为什么会想住在这儿?\NWhy would she want to live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直对她很坏 她肯定恨我们才对\NWe've been awful to her. She must hate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她不恨我们啊 给她次机会吧\NShe doesn't, though. Give her a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我们这边的了\NShe's on our side now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这么容易?哇\NJust like that? Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没可能\NThere's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 你们俩不也是想在这里建立新生活\NWell, you guys wanted to start a new life here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她肯定也想啊\NIt can totally happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就算她想待在这里\NEven if she wants to be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她也理解不了这里的生活\Nshe doesn't know what she's getting into.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,地球生活真的很迷\NLife on Earth is really confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我都花了好长时间才适应\NIt took me a long time to get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在还在适应\NI'm still getting used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-嗯 -但是...\N-Hmm. -But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以教她啊!\Nwe can show her the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 我们已经跨过这个坎了\NI mean, we've been through the ringer on all this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以分享下自己的经验嘛\NIt'll be cool to share what we've learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道 我们肯定会教得很好的\NAnd, you know, I think we'd be really good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,行 我试一试 但是我们得慢慢来\NOkay, I'll give it a try, but we'll have to take it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,棒!\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定很棒的 我就知道!\NThis will be great, I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 谢谢你们!\NWoop! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你是个地球种了!\NSo you're an Earthling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.21,0:04:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这又意味着什么呢?\NBut what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,答案就是...\NWell, the answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢?\Nwho knows?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是地球的美丽之处啦!\NAnd that's the beauty of Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的一切都不合逻辑!\NNothing here makes sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么你需要我们!\NBut that's why you have us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢上地球一开始可能很难\NIt might be hard to like Earth at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就是...\NIt is where...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那些糟糕的事发生的地方\Na bunch of bad stuff happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这儿!这儿好阳光啊!\NI love it! It's so sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对的!\NAh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳--永不熄灭地燃烧...直到熄灭为止\NThe sun -- ever-burning... until it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这个星球上有气象变化\NThis planet has weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候很令人困惑和恐慌\Nwhich can be confusing and alarming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是晴天 但是待会可能会下雨\NIt's sunny now, but it could always rain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什么是"下雨"?\NWhat is rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就像--等下!我可以给你演示\NIt's like -- oh, wait! I can just show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哇!\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道有点奇怪 但是--\NI know it's a bit strange, but --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,天空在哭泣啊!\NThe sky is crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她喜欢这个!脐脐喜欢这个!\NShe likes it! Navy likes it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哦!\NOh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一颗有阴有晴的星球!\NA planet that's not always sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像它...总是在变化!\NIt's almost like it's always...changing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太美了!\NThat's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊!就是这样!\NYeah! Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哇!\NWow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这已经是《地球生活》第97章的内容了\NThat's, like, chapter 97 of Earth stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我们手上有个超前的学生呢!\NLooks like we got an advanced student on our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 不假\NYeah. No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的"宝石洞"\NThis is our "gem cave."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,青金石不喜欢我用这个称呼 我就没用\NLapis hates when I call it that, so I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个仓库挺大的\NThe barn's pretty big,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以随便找个角落\Nso you can have one of the corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,都是你的了\N Make it your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来好棒啊\NThat sounds so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一个角落 太美好了\NAny corner would be lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以到处转转\NYou should have a look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哦!这是干嘛的?\NOhh! What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个吊床 可以从上面掉下来的床\NThat's a hammock. It's a bed you fall out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢在上面睡觉\NIt's where I like to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要睡觉 但是我喜欢睡觉\NI don't have to do it, but I like to do it --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的 放空一切 然后--\Nyou know, turn off for a bit and --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,打呼噜 就像这样\NSnore. Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,呼噜!\NSnore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哇!听起来好炫!我该怎么做?\NWow! Sounds groovy! How do I start?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这个很难解释\NThat one's really hard to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你就躺在那儿 闭上眼\NYou lay down somewhere and close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,然后什么都不想--或者什么都想\NAnd think about nothing -- or everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是可能需要一段时间\NBut it may take you a little while
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你才能感到放松然后--\Nto feel comfortable enough to --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你已经掌握了\NLooks like you've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的有机地球田地\NAnd here's our organic Earth farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们脚下的土壤中充满了资源\NThe ground beneath our feet is teeming with resources
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可以喂饱这些庄稼\Nwhich feed the growing crops around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不用费心和玉米交流了\NDon't bother talking to the corn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,它们听不见\NIt can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你一开始可能会感到植物很陌生 别担心\NPlants may seem strange to you at first, but don't worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不需要立刻就学会喜欢上所有事物\Nyou don't have to love everything right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢植物!哦!\NI love plants! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 那南瓜呢?\NWell, what about Pumpkin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢南瓜吗?\NDo you love Pumpkin, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱南瓜!\NI love Pumpkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,噫 南瓜之吻!\NEw, Pumpkin kisses! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那泥土呢?你也喜欢泥土吗?\NWell, what about dirt? Do you love the dirt, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,泥土是什么?\NWhat's dirt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢泥土!\NI do love the dirt! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们呢?你对我们什么感觉?\NSo what about us? How do you feel about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是最棒的!\NYou guys are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢!谢谢你们!谢谢你们让我加入!\NThank you, thank you! Thank you all for taking me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哦!我们肯定会成为最好的朋友的!\NOh! We're gonna be the best of friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们是敌人啊!\NBut we were just enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得了?你为什么不生气?!\NDon't you remember? Why don't you get mad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我就算试着生气\NI think even if I really tried,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是不会生气的\Nthat's the one thing I can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 得了吧!\NOh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我做错了什么?\NDid I do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可要更复杂一些吧\NI think it might be more complicated than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你待在这里欣赏植物吧\NWhy don't you stay here and admire more of the plants?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-青金石!-青金石!\N-Lapis! -Lapis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-青金石!-青金石!\N-Lapis! -Lapis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-你在哪?!-她简直...\N-Where are you?! -She's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她看起来好像喜欢我们\NIt's just like she's fine with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就像啥事没有一样\Nlike there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,青金石 你还好吗?\NLapis, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不好 我有很严重的问题\NNo. Something is seriously wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我花了那么长时间才喜欢上这个星球\NIt took me so long to learn to like this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 没人说非得那么着急啊\NHey, no one said there's a rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,脐脐就是能很快喜欢上所有人和所有事的那种\NNavy just loves everyone and everything right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,她没防备 也没恐惧 我理解不了\NShe has no guard, no fear. I just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么对她来说那么容易 对我来说那么难?\NWhy is it so easy for her, when it was so hard for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不!\NOh, no! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是有意让你们伤心的!\NI didn't mean to make anyone upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哦!我还是最好离开吧!\NOh! Maybe I should just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-嗷 脐脐 -不 是我的问题\N-Aw, Navy. -No, no, it's my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让你觉得你不属于这里的\NI didn't mean to make you feel like you don't belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 你在这儿就很好!\NYeah, you should stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 大伙儿!我太高兴了!\NOoh, you guys! I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道我还能去哪\NI don't know where I would go anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没了飞船我哪儿也去不了\NI can't go anywhere without my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那儿其实是我唯一的归属了\NThat's the only place I've ever really belonged, anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:09:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我太想它了!哦!\NI miss it so much! Oh! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,脐脐!你的飞船在我们这儿!\NNavy! We have your ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那里!\NIt's right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿?哇!\NYou do? Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我都没注意到它在那儿!\NI didn't even notice it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你可以...让我们参观下你的工作?\NMaybe you could, uh... show us the ropes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我太乐意了!\N I would love that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哦吼吼吼!\NWhoo-hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,简直完美!\NThis is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,水晶宝石们总算有个飞行员了!\NThe Crystal Gems finally have a pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都好 是吧?\NThings are going okay now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 一切都好!\NYeah. Yeah, they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 史蒂文 按一下你后面那个按钮\NHey, Steven, hit that button behind you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我来展示下这架宝贝儿的能力\Nand I'll show you what this baby can really do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 你是说这个按钮?\NUh, you mean the one right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是!就是那个!\NYeah! That's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我要按了!\NI'm gonna press it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,脐脐!你在吗?!\NNavy! Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,脐脐!飞船好像出问题了了!\NNavy, I think something went wrong with the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一的问题是...\NThe only thing wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你们竟然还在扒着\Nis that you're still holding on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,等下!这么久以来 你的唯一目的就是太空船?\NWait! This whole time, all you wanted was your ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你一开始偷走不就好了吗!\NYou could have just stolen it to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然可以啊\NI could have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这样一来 我又怎么\NBut then I would never have gotten to see
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,欣赏你们这些\Nthe look on your face
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,被你们最可爱的红宝石骗之后的傻脸呢\Nwhen you were tricked by your favorite little ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-啥?-嘿!\N-What?! -Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我听不见你们在说啥!\NI can't hear what's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,脐脐是在给我们展示大海吗?\NIs Navy showing us the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哦!这样效果还挺棒呢!\NOh! 'Cause this is a heck of a way to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你个肮脏的小...\NYou dirty, little...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,白白!\NBye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,快 青金石!她要跑了!\NQuick, Lapis, she's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都是对的!\NI was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没人能那么心地善良的\NNo one could be that well-adjusted!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,石榴!\NGarnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,至少心思没白费\NIt was still worth a shot.
